WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.480
Hey, good evening, everybody. I just wanted

00:00:02.159 --> 00:00:04.980
to come on here and talk to you all

00:00:03.480 --> 00:00:06.899
about some things the Lord has been

00:00:04.980 --> 00:00:08.460
speaking to me about through prayer.

00:00:06.899 --> 00:00:10.260
First off, I want to just

00:00:08.460 --> 00:00:12.900
say thank you for all the support that

00:00:10.260 --> 00:00:14.759
I'm getting, all the encouragement, and all

00:00:12.900 --> 00:00:16.440
the blessings—you all keep saying

00:00:14.759 --> 00:00:18.539
'bless you'and all that stuff. There are

00:00:16.440 --> 00:00:20.460
several people who are

00:00:18.539 --> 00:00:22.320
not being too nice, but for the most part,

00:00:20.460 --> 00:00:24.660
I have a lot of support, so I just wanted

00:00:22.320 --> 00:00:27.720
to say thank you. I am not a fortune

00:00:24.660 --> 00:00:30.240
teller. Please do not email my house

00:00:27.720 --> 00:00:32.399
asking for direction concerning your

00:00:30.240 --> 00:00:35.219
life for me to hear God for you.

00:00:32.399 --> 00:00:37.860
My job is to come on here and teach

00:00:35.219 --> 00:00:40.079
you how to do it yourself. You have the

00:00:37.860 --> 00:00:42.239
same Holy Ghost that lives on the inside

00:00:40.079 --> 00:00:44.100
of you that lives on the inside of me.

00:00:42.239 --> 00:00:45.839
People are really concerned about

00:00:44.100 --> 00:00:47.579
the EMP attack; people are really

00:00:45.840 --> 00:00:52.680
concerned about

00:00:47.579 --> 00:00:54.960
the water poisoning.

00:00:52.680 --> 00:00:58.140
Whenever I was taking care of my yard

00:00:54.960 --> 00:01:00.120
work, the Lord spoke to me and

00:00:58.140 --> 00:01:02.460
said there's a shifting.

00:01:00.120 --> 00:01:04.018
I could feel it; there's a pushback of

00:01:02.460 --> 00:01:07.680
the demonic

00:01:04.019 --> 00:01:10.020
assignment that was upon America. Our

00:01:07.680 --> 00:01:12.659
prayers are working, and he reminded me,

00:01:10.020 --> 00:01:15.179
'Brandon, I called you and put you

00:01:12.659 --> 00:01:17.340
on there for prayer.'That was your main

00:01:15.180 --> 00:01:19.979
assignment: to teach the people to pray,

00:01:17.340 --> 00:01:21.659
putting videos of prayer so that they

00:01:19.979 --> 00:01:25.140
could jump in the rivers.

00:01:21.659 --> 00:01:28.619
We are a mighty force together when we

00:01:25.140 --> 00:01:30.900
are praying as a unit, not like, as I

00:01:28.619 --> 00:01:32.880
said, Rambos out there

00:01:30.900 --> 00:01:35.700
trying to fight the war by themselves.

00:01:32.880 --> 00:01:38.759
If we will come together and fight

00:01:35.700 --> 00:01:42.180
together, we're able to move mountains, and

00:01:38.759 --> 00:01:44.640
it's amazing what we can accomplish

00:01:42.180 --> 00:01:46.979
just with five minutes of prayer a day.

00:01:44.640 --> 00:01:49.799
I'm not bringing it in, as I said, for

00:01:46.979 --> 00:01:53.340
fear; I'm bringing this to you to help me

00:01:49.799 --> 00:01:55.560
pray. It's not drama. So, here you

00:01:53.340 --> 00:01:57.000
go: I want to come on here and I want to

00:01:55.560 --> 00:01:58.320
tell you all some things now about what

00:01:57.000 --> 00:02:00.540
the Lord is showing me in prayer. First

00:01:58.320 --> 00:02:02.220
off, I want to tell you all some

00:02:00.540 --> 00:02:04.140
positive things, something that happened

00:02:02.220 --> 00:02:06.600
that was a birthday present to me from

00:02:04.140 --> 00:02:07.740
the Lord. When I was praying, all of a

00:02:06.600 --> 00:02:10.199
sudden, he said, 'I want to give you a

00:02:07.740 --> 00:02:12.359
birthday present, Brandon.'And I said, 'Oh,

00:02:10.199 --> 00:02:15.000
wow, what is it, Lord?'Then all of a

00:02:12.360 --> 00:02:17.940
sudden, he opened my eyes in the

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:21.360
spirit and he showed me right after the

00:02:17.940 --> 00:02:22.620
Rapture happens. I was standing in

00:02:21.360 --> 00:02:25.319
heaven,

00:02:22.620 --> 00:02:28.379
and I was on this green field. It was

00:02:25.319 --> 00:02:30.780
beautiful. There were hills all

00:02:28.379 --> 00:02:33.299
up in front of me and I could see

00:02:30.780 --> 00:02:35.520
mountains all in the distance. There was

00:02:33.300 --> 00:02:36.900
snow on top of these mountains, which is

00:02:35.520 --> 00:02:39.540
really amazing. This was happening—it

00:02:36.900 --> 00:02:43.620
looked like the Swiss Alps.

00:02:39.540 --> 00:02:45.840
It was gorgeous all in the distance.

00:02:43.620 --> 00:02:49.620
These green pastures were

00:02:45.840 --> 00:02:51.420
all before me. The grass was so green it

00:02:49.620 --> 00:02:54.720
looked

00:02:51.420 --> 00:02:57.480
almost transparent. It was beautiful

00:02:54.720 --> 00:03:00.000
green grass. I have never seen this kind

00:02:57.480 --> 00:03:02.819
of grass on the earth, how beautiful and

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:05.340
lush and green this was. My wife was

00:03:02.819 --> 00:03:07.560
running in from the distance and she was

00:03:05.340 --> 00:03:09.840
doing cartwheels. We were in our

00:03:07.560 --> 00:03:13.519
glorified bodies. I could see I was

00:03:09.840 --> 00:03:17.040
skinny and I had hair,

00:03:13.519 --> 00:03:19.440
but my face didn't look hard, as if

00:03:17.040 --> 00:03:22.079
I'd been through a lot. It was

00:03:19.440 --> 00:03:25.379
so young and youthful; it was

00:03:22.080 --> 00:03:26.700
beautiful. Everything I was seeing—I

00:03:25.379 --> 00:03:28.980
could see my wife, and she was doing

00:03:26.700 --> 00:03:31.140
cartwheels like I said. She ran into

00:03:28.980 --> 00:03:33.659
me and she goes, 'Brandon, we made it! It

00:03:31.140 --> 00:03:35.700
really happened.'And I kept saying, 'It

00:03:33.659 --> 00:03:37.859
really happened. We made it.'I could

00:03:35.700 --> 00:03:40.140
see the glory; you could feel the

00:03:37.860 --> 00:03:42.900
presence of glory. There were no shadows

00:03:40.140 --> 00:03:44.879
on anything; the light was so beautiful

00:03:42.900 --> 00:03:46.739
and so bright.

00:03:44.879 --> 00:03:47.819
Sorry, my dog is running in the back playing with a

00:03:46.739 --> 00:03:48.840
toy, if you heard that

00:03:47.819 --> 00:03:50.760
squeaking.

00:03:48.840 --> 00:03:54.560
There was a glorious

00:03:50.760 --> 00:03:57.239
light all around everything and

00:03:54.560 --> 00:04:00.060
heaven. I just wanted to come on

00:03:57.239 --> 00:04:02.280
and tell you all, we're about to be

00:04:00.060 --> 00:04:04.080
there. We're almost there; we're right

00:04:02.280 --> 00:04:06.120
at the finish line, guys. We just got

00:04:04.080 --> 00:04:07.860
to push just a little bit harder here. We

00:04:06.120 --> 00:04:09.900
got to pray, and God's going to do some

00:04:07.860 --> 00:04:11.459
great things in this earth still with a

00:04:09.900 --> 00:04:13.080
revival. There's going to be some people

00:04:11.459 --> 00:04:14.939
He's going to bring in that have been wayward—the

00:04:13.080 --> 00:04:16.739
children that are wayward.

00:04:14.939 --> 00:04:18.298
Like I said, the moms are

00:04:16.738 --> 00:04:19.978
praying, and they're calling out

00:04:18.298 --> 00:04:22.198
and asking God for their kids to get

00:04:19.978 --> 00:04:24.300
born again. I'm telling you, don't give up on

00:04:22.199 --> 00:04:26.880
those children

00:04:24.300 --> 00:04:28.680
that are wayward. The Lord hears your

00:04:26.880 --> 00:04:30.659
prayers, and He's bringing those kids in.

00:04:28.680 --> 00:04:32.580
I'm telling you, you just got to keep the

00:04:30.660 --> 00:04:34.020
faith and keep standing, and there's

00:04:32.580 --> 00:04:36.240
going to be a breakthrough in your

00:04:34.020 --> 00:04:38.639
household. I'm telling you, you just got

00:04:36.240 --> 00:04:41.460
to keep on. When all else there is

00:04:38.639 --> 00:04:42.540
to do is stand, stand therefore. Do not

00:04:41.460 --> 00:04:44.880
give up

00:04:42.540 --> 00:04:47.100
for your healings, for the miracles

00:04:44.880 --> 00:04:49.259
that you're believing for, or for

00:04:47.100 --> 00:04:51.720
finances. You may not have anything to

00:04:49.259 --> 00:04:53.820
eat, but my God said He's never seen the

00:04:51.720 --> 00:04:55.919
righteous forsaken or his seed begging

00:04:53.820 --> 00:04:57.479
bread. He'll bring forth the finances

00:04:55.919 --> 00:05:00.479
that you need.

00:04:57.479 --> 00:05:03.360
I just believe in a faithful God; if He

00:05:00.479 --> 00:05:05.820
would bring the raven to feed Elijah,

00:05:03.360 --> 00:05:07.259
He'll bring a raven to feed

00:05:05.820 --> 00:05:10.320
you.

00:05:07.259 --> 00:05:12.540
Now, I just want to tell you all what

00:05:10.320 --> 00:05:14.880
the Lord has warned me about what's

00:05:12.540 --> 00:05:18.020
coming and what we can avoid in prayer

00:05:14.880 --> 00:05:20.159
and what we can stop.

00:05:18.020 --> 00:05:23.758
Excuse me,

00:05:20.160 --> 00:05:25.860
I saw...

00:05:23.759 --> 00:05:28.380
this is something that reminded

00:05:25.860 --> 00:05:29.460
me when I was doing my yard

00:05:28.380 --> 00:05:31.500
work tonight. This is what I'm trying to

00:05:29.460 --> 00:05:34.020
tell you. He said, 'I want you to tell

00:05:31.500 --> 00:05:37.620
them to pray for Donald Trump.'I saw him

00:05:34.020 --> 00:05:39.659
walking down on a cobblestone path. I saw

00:05:37.620 --> 00:05:43.380
it was like tropical—I don't know where

00:05:39.660 --> 00:05:45.720
he was—but I saw a woman. Now, sometimes

00:05:43.380 --> 00:05:48.539
I'm seeing in the spirit and it's not

00:05:45.720 --> 00:05:51.240
necessarily... this

00:05:48.539 --> 00:05:53.340
warning that the

00:05:51.240 --> 00:05:55.860
Lord has told me about was about

00:05:53.340 --> 00:05:57.419
Donald Trump and to intercede and

00:05:55.860 --> 00:06:01.080
pray for him.

00:05:57.419 --> 00:06:04.380
He showed me him walking down a

00:06:01.080 --> 00:06:07.380
cobblestone path. Now, I don't know

00:06:04.380 --> 00:06:09.300
if this is legitimately a cobblestone

00:06:07.380 --> 00:06:11.039
path or if

00:06:09.300 --> 00:06:14.160
it's like a type and shadow of something.

00:06:11.039 --> 00:06:16.380
He's walking down this path, and

00:06:14.160 --> 00:06:18.600
this woman is

00:06:16.380 --> 00:06:20.880
absolutely beautiful. She has

00:06:18.600 --> 00:06:22.979
blonde hair in a French twist

00:06:20.880 --> 00:06:26.400
and she was dressed

00:06:22.979 --> 00:06:29.758
up in a beautiful dress. She

00:06:26.400 --> 00:06:32.940
was there to take him out.

00:06:29.759 --> 00:06:34.860
The Secret

00:06:32.940 --> 00:06:37.620
Service people around were

00:06:34.860 --> 00:06:40.380
not guarded because of this

00:06:37.620 --> 00:06:43.139
woman's beauty; she was very

00:06:40.380 --> 00:06:44.940
classy. I don't know if this is a

00:06:43.139 --> 00:06:47.400
type and shadow of someone who

00:06:44.940 --> 00:06:49.500
would try to

00:06:47.400 --> 00:06:51.960
seduce him,

00:06:49.500 --> 00:06:55.199
but this woman was an assignment

00:06:51.960 --> 00:06:56.460
against him. This

00:06:55.199 --> 00:06:59.340
is something I'm praying

00:06:56.460 --> 00:07:02.818
over: protection for God to deliver

00:06:59.340 --> 00:07:05.580
him from either a seducing spirit, like a

00:07:02.819 --> 00:07:08.039
Jezebel kind of person, or an actual

00:07:05.580 --> 00:07:09.780
attempt on him.

00:07:08.039 --> 00:07:11.880
This is very serious. The Lord has

00:07:09.780 --> 00:07:14.340
had me praying for his protection from

00:07:11.880 --> 00:07:16.680
an assignment involving

00:07:14.340 --> 00:07:19.560
this beautiful woman. She has blonde hair

00:07:16.680 --> 00:07:23.520
and

00:07:19.560 --> 00:07:25.680
looks very much like a

00:07:23.520 --> 00:07:27.599
model. This

00:07:25.680 --> 00:07:28.979
was part of something

00:07:27.599 --> 00:07:31.800
the Lord had me interceding for. Lately,

00:07:28.979 --> 00:07:33.599
He had me praying for

00:07:33.599 --> 00:07:40.199
this oil tanker that was in the Atlantic

00:07:36.960 --> 00:07:42.180
Ocean coming out of Africa.

00:07:40.199 --> 00:07:44.039
This is something else; it's

00:07:42.180 --> 00:07:46.800
not about fear, it's just something

00:07:44.039 --> 00:07:48.919
I pray over. You are prayer

00:07:46.800 --> 00:07:51.660
warriors,

00:07:48.919 --> 00:07:53.159
and you can help me. This

00:07:51.660 --> 00:07:54.180
could be something way off in the

00:07:53.160 --> 00:07:56.340
distance or something

00:07:54.180 --> 00:07:58.860
we've already stopped, but I bring

00:07:56.340 --> 00:08:01.138
these things out here. If you feel

00:07:58.860 --> 00:08:03.419
led to pray over it, pray; if not,

00:08:01.139 --> 00:08:07.020
put it on a shelf and walk away. This was

00:08:03.419 --> 00:08:10.440
an oil tanker coming out of Africa, and

00:08:07.020 --> 00:08:12.900
all of the crew on board were rounded

00:08:10.440 --> 00:08:14.699
up by these terrorists.

00:08:12.900 --> 00:08:16.620
They were hiding on the ship,

00:08:14.699 --> 00:08:18.360
got on board, took

00:08:16.620 --> 00:08:20.099
these men to the bottom of the ship,

00:08:18.360 --> 00:08:24.599
and killed them.

00:08:20.099 --> 00:08:26.460
I saw them with a briefcase—I'm

00:08:24.599 --> 00:08:29.280
not going to say the word—but

00:08:26.460 --> 00:08:31.258
it's very

00:08:29.280 --> 00:08:34.319
powerful.

00:08:31.259 --> 00:08:38.760
They took the ship to

00:08:34.320 --> 00:08:41.219
Washington Harbor,

00:08:38.760 --> 00:08:43.919
near

00:08:41.219 --> 00:08:45.600
Virginia. I'm going to show you on a map

00:08:43.919 --> 00:08:48.060
right now.

00:08:48.060 --> 00:08:54.000
They brought the ship in and

00:08:51.420 --> 00:08:56.699
set this thing off.

00:08:54.000 --> 00:08:59.160
It was very serious

00:08:56.700 --> 00:09:02.160
and powerful;

00:08:59.160 --> 00:09:04.319
everything

00:09:02.160 --> 00:09:06.360
went away. I'm trying to

00:09:04.320 --> 00:09:09.060
say this in a way that doesn't get me

00:09:06.360 --> 00:09:10.680
flagged. I just wanted

00:09:09.060 --> 00:09:12.540
to come on here and

00:09:10.680 --> 00:09:14.880
tell you these are more things

00:09:12.540 --> 00:09:18.719
I'm praying over.

00:09:14.880 --> 00:09:21.000
We live in dangerous and

00:09:18.720 --> 00:09:23.339
challenging times. I do

00:09:21.000 --> 00:09:26.160
not live in a fairytale land where

00:09:23.339 --> 00:09:28.620
everything is always okay.

00:09:26.160 --> 00:09:31.439
I wake up every day and

00:09:28.620 --> 00:09:34.200
the Lord has me on assignments. I am

00:09:31.440 --> 00:09:36.779
on missions, praying for things on a

00:09:34.200 --> 00:09:39.180
continual basis for what He has for the

00:09:36.779 --> 00:09:43.320
end times, for the church, and for

00:09:39.180 --> 00:09:45.959
the thousand years. We

00:09:43.320 --> 00:09:49.080
have a bright future ahead of us; God has

00:09:45.959 --> 00:09:52.079
a great plan for us. Lastly,

00:09:49.080 --> 00:09:54.740
He had me pray against large

00:09:52.080 --> 00:10:00.060
gatherings of people

00:09:54.740 --> 00:10:02.820
for mass shootings. Pray

00:10:00.060 --> 00:10:06.359
against this; it's an

00:10:02.820 --> 00:10:08.820
assignment being sent to try

00:10:06.360 --> 00:10:12.660
to take the Second Amendment away from

00:10:08.820 --> 00:10:17.940
the people. And they're going to

00:10:12.660 --> 00:10:19.860
run on campaigns in 2024; a lot of it

00:10:17.940 --> 00:10:22.140
will be ran against the Second Amendment

00:10:19.860 --> 00:10:25.860
and taking things away.

00:10:22.140 --> 00:10:27.839
I saw these big mass events

00:10:25.860 --> 00:10:30.839
trying to take place. The Lord had me

00:10:27.839 --> 00:10:32.279
pray very hard for Coachella. I kept

00:10:30.839 --> 00:10:34.500
praying for this word, 'Coachella,'and

00:10:32.279 --> 00:10:36.420
I kept getting this in the

00:10:34.500 --> 00:10:37.980
spirit realm. So I told my friend about

00:10:36.420 --> 00:10:40.079
it and he helped me Google it, and then

00:10:37.980 --> 00:10:42.480
my wife helped me Google this word.

00:10:40.080 --> 00:10:44.519
It was days away from what was

00:10:42.480 --> 00:10:48.180
supposed to take place, and I interceded

00:10:44.519 --> 00:10:50.399
for this hard. I prayed a fast,

00:10:48.180 --> 00:10:52.500
believing God for protection so that this

00:10:50.399 --> 00:10:54.120
stuff didn't happen. Nothing happened. Now,

00:10:52.500 --> 00:10:56.459
I don't know when it happens again; I

00:10:54.120 --> 00:10:58.920
believe probably next year. So we're

00:10:56.459 --> 00:11:01.979
going to pray that these major events and

00:10:58.920 --> 00:11:05.699
big gatherings of people for nothing to

00:11:01.980 --> 00:11:08.519
happen. If you have a check in

00:11:05.700 --> 00:11:11.880
your spirit about major gatherings, do

00:11:08.519 --> 00:11:13.440
not go. Pray in the Holy Ghost and the

00:11:11.880 --> 00:11:16.620
Lord will protect you.

00:11:13.440 --> 00:11:19.680
Use wisdom in this day and hour for you and

00:11:16.620 --> 00:11:22.560
for your family to not just be

00:11:19.680 --> 00:11:25.800
flippantly going places.

00:11:22.560 --> 00:11:28.199
Pray ahead of time: 'Lord, is it Your will

00:11:25.800 --> 00:11:31.380
for me to go to that concert? Is it Your

00:11:28.200 --> 00:11:33.240
will for me to go to that sporting event?'Because

00:11:31.380 --> 00:11:35.399
if you don't and you

00:11:33.240 --> 00:11:37.800
hear the Lord not to go,

00:11:35.399 --> 00:11:41.399
it could cost you your life. You have to

00:11:37.800 --> 00:11:44.219
be very vigilant nowadays in prayer and

00:11:41.399 --> 00:11:46.860
fasting, listening to Him on where you're

00:11:44.220 --> 00:11:48.600
supposed to be at all times. Don't just

00:11:46.860 --> 00:11:50.640
go to malls; do not just go to

00:11:48.600 --> 00:11:52.320
certain things without hearing Him on that

00:11:50.640 --> 00:11:54.959
day. Wake up that morning and say,

00:11:52.320 --> 00:11:57.540
'Father, what am I supposed to do? What's

00:11:54.959 --> 00:11:59.640
Your agenda for me, not what's my agenda?'You listen to

00:11:57.540 --> 00:12:02.160
Him

00:11:59.640 --> 00:12:04.860
for your life.

00:12:02.160 --> 00:12:07.560
'Lord, can I go to the grocery store

00:12:04.860 --> 00:12:09.839
today? Can I go to the

00:12:07.560 --> 00:12:10.979
game? Can I go to this and

00:12:09.839 --> 00:12:14.579
that?'Ask

00:12:10.980 --> 00:12:16.920
Him; He will guide you on every step

00:12:14.579 --> 00:12:19.560
you're supposed to take for your life

00:12:16.920 --> 00:12:21.779
that day, every day.

00:12:19.560 --> 00:12:24.300
He wants to be that close to

00:12:21.779 --> 00:12:26.040
you. Let Him speak to you and practice His

00:12:24.300 --> 00:12:28.439
presence.

00:12:26.040 --> 00:12:31.260
A lot of people always ask me,

00:12:28.440 --> 00:12:33.300
'How do you hear God the way you do? How

00:12:31.260 --> 00:12:36.180
do you listen to Him like that?'It

00:12:33.300 --> 00:12:38.160
started like this.

00:12:36.180 --> 00:12:40.260
He told me, 'I'm going to start

00:12:38.160 --> 00:12:42.540
talking to you about things, and I want

00:12:40.260 --> 00:12:44.939
you to practice My voice. I want you

00:12:42.540 --> 00:12:47.040
to practice this.'It was just private

00:12:44.940 --> 00:12:48.420
between me and Him, and He said, 'I'm going

00:12:47.040 --> 00:12:51.540
to tell you about sports

00:12:48.420 --> 00:12:54.779
because I love sports.'It's one of my big things—football,

00:12:51.540 --> 00:12:56.579
basketball, baseball, all

00:12:54.779 --> 00:12:58.620
of it. I watch it, I love it, it's amazing

00:12:56.579 --> 00:13:01.979
to me. You know, just the game; I love the

00:12:58.620 --> 00:13:03.959
testosterone of it. And so,

00:13:01.980 --> 00:13:06.920
we would sit on the couch together, the

00:13:03.959 --> 00:13:10.500
Lord and I, and He would talk to me about

00:13:06.920 --> 00:13:12.540
the score. He'd say, 'This is who's

00:13:10.500 --> 00:13:14.100
going to win, and this is the score, and this is how

00:13:12.540 --> 00:13:15.480
much they're going to win by—this

00:13:14.100 --> 00:13:16.860
team and this team.'He'd tell me the

00:13:15.480 --> 00:13:18.839
game for that day, college football or

00:13:16.860 --> 00:13:20.459
whatever, and He said, 'This is who's going

00:13:18.839 --> 00:13:22.019
to win it, and this is how much they're

00:13:20.459 --> 00:13:24.359
going to win it by.'He talked about Super

00:13:22.019 --> 00:13:27.120
Bowls, He talks about World Series, He

00:13:24.360 --> 00:13:29.100
talks about it all. And so I practice His

00:13:27.120 --> 00:13:31.019
presence; I practice His voice.

00:13:29.100 --> 00:13:34.740
He said to me, 'If

00:13:31.019 --> 00:13:36.839
you ever bet or gamble on anything I

00:13:34.740 --> 00:13:39.420
ever tell you, I will not talk this way

00:13:36.839 --> 00:13:41.459
to you ever again. But I want you to go

00:13:39.420 --> 00:13:44.120
like you're going to a

00:13:41.459 --> 00:13:46.739
spiritual gym. I want you to work out

00:13:44.120 --> 00:13:49.200
that muscle, your

00:13:46.740 --> 00:13:51.839
spiritual ears, with Me.'And

00:13:49.200 --> 00:13:54.060
this is how I started: I practice His

00:13:51.839 --> 00:13:57.540
presence. Then He talks to me about the

00:13:54.060 --> 00:14:00.300
weather. He says, 'In six weeks, it's going to

00:13:57.540 --> 00:14:01.920
be this temperature outside;

00:14:00.300 --> 00:14:03.839
it's going to snow, and this is how much we're going to get.'He

00:14:01.920 --> 00:14:06.000
talks to me about how much rain we're going to

00:14:03.839 --> 00:14:07.500
get. He talks to me about when the

00:14:06.000 --> 00:14:10.139
fall will start, when the first cold

00:14:07.500 --> 00:14:11.459
front's going to come, and He tells me way

00:14:10.139 --> 00:14:13.380
in advance. He said, 'I want you to

00:14:11.459 --> 00:14:15.479
write this down.'He said summer's going to

00:14:13.380 --> 00:14:17.459
have this many hurricanes, and in

00:14:15.480 --> 00:14:19.440
the Gulf Coast, this is how many

00:14:17.459 --> 00:14:21.239
hurricanes are going to be here and this is

00:14:19.440 --> 00:14:22.920
how big they're going to be. You can pray

00:14:21.240 --> 00:14:25.200
against them, pray for safety for people,

00:14:22.920 --> 00:14:27.420
and He will show me. Then He shows me

00:14:25.200 --> 00:14:30.000
about tornado season; He shows me about

00:14:27.420 --> 00:14:32.660
the storms. That's how I've learned

00:14:30.000 --> 00:14:35.579
to develop my spiritual ears,

00:14:32.660 --> 00:14:37.620
practicing His presence. And sometimes

00:14:35.579 --> 00:14:40.138
you miss it. It's okay;

00:14:37.620 --> 00:14:41.760
we're human. But you just keep picking

00:14:40.139 --> 00:14:43.380
yourself back up and say, 'Lord, I missed

00:14:41.760 --> 00:14:45.060
that. I thought I

00:14:43.380 --> 00:14:46.980
heard You right on that, but I didn't.'And

00:14:45.060 --> 00:14:48.959
you humble yourself and you keep

00:14:46.980 --> 00:14:51.120
going. You don't kick

00:14:48.959 --> 00:14:52.680
yourself when you fall down; you rise

00:14:51.120 --> 00:14:55.440
back up.

00:14:52.680 --> 00:14:56.579
You have to keep on keeping on.

00:14:56.579 --> 00:15:00.000
We all have a tendency; we can miss it.

00:14:58.740 --> 00:15:02.279
I'm going to tell you

00:15:00.000 --> 00:15:04.620
right off: I've missed it a lot on

00:15:02.279 --> 00:15:06.540
things when I was first starting out,

00:15:04.620 --> 00:15:09.540
about investments and the timing of things,

00:15:06.540 --> 00:15:10.620
and

00:15:10.620 --> 00:15:15.839
it's okay. That's how we learn.

00:15:13.380 --> 00:15:18.180
I just want to encourage

00:15:15.839 --> 00:15:21.240
you all.

00:15:18.180 --> 00:15:23.819
God is a graceful God. He's not mad;

00:15:21.240 --> 00:15:26.760
he's not up there beating people up. He is

00:15:23.820 --> 00:15:28.440
a lot of love. I just

00:15:26.760 --> 00:15:30.000
wanted to encourage you with that. That

00:15:28.440 --> 00:15:34.459
was another thing I wanted to tell you.

00:15:30.000 --> 00:15:34.459
Have a blessed day, everybody. Bye-bye.

